allParagraphs: They are not compulsory but use them to prepare your labs or for additional help outside the scope of your lab e.g. setting up your laptop for home computing. There will be additional tutors during assignments. Attend if you are stuck on your assignments.
Check back here regularly. More help time slots may be added as assignment deadlines approaches.
